Perhaps.. a friend

902
01:25:47,467 --> 01:25:49,435
Birjoo. Hey, Birjoo

903
01:25:52,172 --> 01:25:54,163
Guess what happened, just guess

904
01:25:54,240 --> 01:25:57,539
Half an hour ago, we were in a
meeting, me, my brother, the managers

905
