943
01:29:37,530 --> 01:29:40,658
And you know, when you
return a victor,

944
01:29:42,101 --> 01:29:46,629
everyone will be waiting with garlands
at the airport, to welcome you

945
01:29:49,175 --> 01:29:50,767
