calls, no letters

953
01:30:22,075 --> 01:30:23,303
Be prepared

954
01:30:25,612 --> 01:30:27,580
I accept. Anything else?

955
01:30:33,152 --> 01:30:36,315
You are here? Everyone's waiting
for you, for the meeting

956
01:30:37,190 --> 01:30:40,626
Go.. I love you dearly

957
01:31:31,644 --> 01:31:34,272
Awake.. at this hour?

958
01:31:36,182 --> 01:31:37,342
I have the right

959
01:31:40,486 --> 01:31:43,319
Waiting for someone
gives such pleasure?

960
01:31:43,389 --> 01:31:45,721
That only a woman's heart would know

961
01:31:47,093 --> 01:31:48,219
Ready to leave?

962
01:31:49,195 --> 01:31:50,662
Yes

963
01:31:52,498 --> 01:31:54,022
