968
01:32:08,448 --> 01:32:10,075
I love you

969
01:32:21,594 --> 01:32:23,687
Rama, Agra was the right place to go.

970
01:32:24,163 --> 01:32:27,428
We got the musicians,
also confectioners

971
01:32:27,500 --> 01:32:31,061
The same confectioner,
whom you favor too

972
01:32:32,138 --> 01:32:34,197
Everyone will land up two or
three days before the wedding

973
01:32:35,241 --> 01:32:37,573
Imagine in less than two months,
Bitto will be a bride

974
01:32:44,083 --> 01:32:45,209
Aunty, you asked for me?

975
01:32:46,486 --> 01:32:48,386
