- Sure. Please, don't harass him

1260
01:56:07,419 --> 01:56:11,150
Wait.. what's the purpose
of this make up?

1261
01:56:11,222 --> 01:56:14,680
To make you look worthy enough
for your pretty wife-to-be

1262
01:56:15,226 --> 01:56:18,957
Really? Then let's have some more
here.. and here.. and here

1263
01:56:19,030 --> 01:56:20,258
Naughty

1264
01:56:21,032 --> 01:56:24,490
May the henna turn a lovely crimson
on your hands, o'bride

1265
01:56:24,569 --> 01:56:28,699
And fetch to you, your lover forever

1266
01:56:29,040 --> 01:56:33,170
Of many fortunes the henna begets,
the most precious is.. eternal love

1267
01:56:35,313 --> 01:56:37,645
Is this all right..?

1268
01:56:39,384 --> 01:56:42,547
It's the fourth time you've tried it.
Hurry, I got to finish packing

1269
01:56:42,620 --> 01:56:45,248
Else, the bridegroom's party will
leave without the bridegroom

1270
01:56:50,228 --> 01:56:52,162
Come Sister-in-law, I'll paint
your hands with henna

1271
01:56:55,400 --> 01:56:57,231
Sister-in-law.. come, join us

1272
01:56:58,570 --> 01:57:00,265
This ritual is too painfully
long for me

1273
01:57:07,145 --> 01:57:11,241
We sing glories of the
Daughter of the hills,

1274
01:57:14,118 --> 01:57:18,179
whose beauty holds Shiva enthralled

1275
01:57:18,256 --> 01:57:22,488
Today we seek Gauri Maa's blessings,

1276
01:57:23,094 --> 01:57:26,962
who revels in Shiva's love forever

1277
01:57:33,137 --> 01:57:37,403
Oh Goddess, You are resplendent
in vermilion,

1278
01:57:37,475 --> 01:57:41,673
Oh Goddess, You are resplendent
in vermilion,

1279
01:57:42,146 --> 01:57:47,140
You wear the bride's reds, Your
palms adorned in crimson henna

1280
01:57:47,218 --> 01:57:51,587
red is Your veil ; redden vermilion
streaks Your hair,

1281
01:57:51,656 --> 01:57:56,423
the red dot on Your forehead,
fragrant with musk

1282
01:57:56,494 --> 01:58:01,295
We pray to You, pour
our emotions to You

1283
01:58:04,135 --> 01:58:07,696
Krishnakant, the rituals have begun,
but I don't see Sister-in-law..?

1284
01:58:09,574 --> 01:58:10,734
I'll fetch her

1285
01:58:12,176 --> 01:58:16,272
O Giver of every wish,

1286
01:58:18,616 --> 01:58:22,677
Keep the bride happy always

1287
01:58:23,521 --> 01:58:27,321
Hail Gauri Mother.
Hail Gauri Mother..

1288
01:58:28,159 --> 01:58:31,390
What is it? Is it the pain
in the knee again?

1289
01:58:41,439 --> 01:58:42,770
Massage it with the balm

1290
01:58:53,117 --> 01:58:57,383
Rama, you did not even look at Poonam's
wedding dress ; I said nothing

1291
01:58:59,223 --> 01:59:03,489
You didn't participate in any of the
wedding rituals ; I said nothing

1292
01:59:04,729 --> 01:59:05,787
But Rama tomorrow..

1293
01:59:07,231 --> 01:59:08,755
tomorrow, Bitto will be leaving
this house forever

1294
01:59:18,343 --> 01:59:20,573
Tomorrow, the bridegroom's party will
come to our door, just like this,

1295
01:59:20,645 --> 01:59:23,136
with a band playing songs of joy

1296
01:59:23,214 --> 01:59:25,739
Give the bride a happy send-off, Rama

1297
01:59:26,184 --> 01:59:28,311
Rama you know this, as I know

1298
01:59:28,386 --> 01:59:31,617
If she is denied your blessings, it
won't be a happy send-off for her

1299
01:59:31,689 --> 01:59:33,020
For once, forget all else Rama,

1300
01:59:33,091 --> 01:59:35,184
for the sake of Poonam's happiness,

1301
01:59:35,259 --> 01:59:42,097
Iet her depart with the belief that
her mother has blessed her way

1302
01:59:44,502 --> 01:59:47,130
All her life, she has yearned
for that one smile of yours

1303
01:59:48,272 --> 01:59:52,038
It's for the child's joy ;
even if we do something..

1304
01:59:52,110 --> 01:59:54,203
.. we dislike, we won't lose face

1305
01:59:56,381 --> 01:59:59,612
But why such resentment, because
she isn't your daughter?

1306
02:00:01,519 --> 02:00:02,645
Better, you do not hear the reply

1307
02:00:08,126 --> 02:00:09,388
Remember Rama..?

1308
02:00:10,495 --> 02:00:14,989
Whenever your knee was in pain, it
was Poonam giving you a massage

1309
02:00:15,066 --> 02:00:16,590
Enough

1310
02:00:19,170 --> 02:00:26,008
Today, you refuse to acknowledge her.
But mind you, when she leaves us..

1311
02:00:26,077 --> 02:00:28,170
you will cry the most

1312
02:00:40,425 --> 02:00:43,553
I am your Mother,

1313
02:00:43,628 --> 02:00:47,189
you are my daughter

1314
02:00:47,265 --> 02:00:50,098
Our bond..

1315
02:00:50,168 --> 02:00:53,535
forever,

1316
02:00:54,639 --> 02:00:57,608
holds us together

1317
02:00:57,675 --> 02:01:01,577
In this home, you shall
never be a stranger..

1318
02:01:01,646 --> 02:01:05,047
though you go to make another
home for yourself

1319
02:01:05,116 --> 02:01:07,050
In both homes, truly..

1320
02:01:07,118 --> 02:01:08,244
you'll belong forever

1321
02:01:57,201 --> 02:02:00,034
Make sure you're done with making
the sweets tonight..

1322
02:02:00,104 --> 02:02:01,731
we're cooking for 400 guests,

1323
02:02:02,206 --> 02:02:05,198
there should be no shortages..
the guests are coming from Delhi

1324
02:02:09,380 --> 02:02:10,472
Chhote Babu..

1325
02:02:13,551 --> 02:02:16,486
Chhote Babu.. fire!
The house is on fire

1326
02:02:32,170 --> 02:02:33,330
Chhote Babu..

1327
02:02:33,404 --> 02:02:34,462
Fire!

1328
02:02:34,539 --> 02:02:36,564
It's a fire!
- Everyone.. out!

1329
02:02:36,641 --> 02:02:39,132
Out.. everyone outside

1330
02:02:45,082 --> 02:02:46,515
Hurry!

1331
02:02:46,584 --> 02:02:48,017
But how did all this..
- All questions later..

1332
02:02:48,085 --> 02:02:49,211
Get out, first

1333
02:02:49,287 --> 02:02:51,448
Water! Douse the fire!

1334
02:03:02,166 --> 02:03:04,498
Quick.. more water! Hurry!

1335
02:03:04,569 --> 02:03:06,730
Bhagat! Where are Chhoti and
Bitto? - Chhoti and Bitto..?

1336
02:03:10,041 --> 02:03:11,474
Somebody save the bride!

1337
02:03:12,043 --> 02:03:13,408
Bitto!

1338
02:03:29,060 --> 02:03:30,322
Uncle

1339
02:03:30,394 --> 02:03:32,055
Don't panic..

1340
02:03:32,129 --> 02:03:34,120
walk to the door

1341
02:03:36,167 --> 02:03:37,327
Stay back

1342
02:03:42,473 --> 02:03:43,667
Quick!

1343
02:03:46,410 --> 02:03:47,570
Your wedding dress?

1344
02:03:57,188 --> 02:03:58,348
Make way for the bride

1345
02:04:01,626 --> 02:04:03,457
Where is Chhoti.. where is Chhoti?

1346
02:04:03,527 --> 02:04:05,757
She must be inside..?
- No, she isn't.. go find her

1347
02:04:06,197 --> 02:04:07,289
Chhoti..?

1348
02:04:08,432 --> 02:04:09,592
Chhoti..!

1349
02:04:20,444 --> 02:04:23,140
Munim.. Chhoti..?
- I've no idea

1350
02:04:23,214 --> 02:04:27,446
Listen.. I think I saw
her going up the stairs

1351
02:04:30,154 --> 02:04:31,712
Listen.. Bitto.. wait!

1352
02:04:37,161 --> 02:04:38,560
Where are you going, Bitto?

1353
02:04:38,629 --> 02:04:39,721
Stop

1354
02:04:46,537 --> 02:04:48,437
Krishnakant.. Krishnakant..

1355
02:04:48,506 --> 02:04:49,700
Chhoti

1356
02:05:07,191 --> 02:05:08,351
Chhoti

1357
02:05:21,305 --> 02:05:22,431
Sister

1358
02:05:50,401 --> 02:05:51,561
Leave me!

1359
02:06:03,414 --> 02:06:06,178
Chhoti.. Chhoti..

1360
02:06:06,250 --> 02:06:08,115
Aunty,

1361
02:06:30,141 --> 02:06:31,301
Aunty,

1362
02:06:31,375 --> 02:06:32,433
Chhoti is fine,

1363
02:06:32,510 --> 02:06:33,568
she's all right

1364
02:06:35,112 --> 02:06:36,306
Poonam

1365
02:06:38,983 --> 02:06:40,177
Chhoti!

1366
02:07:09,080 --> 02:07:10,445
Call Dr Rashid, a burns case is here

1367
02:07:18,422 --> 02:07:22,654
The patient has severe burns, Doctor.
- Okay, let's go

1368
02:08:00,431 --> 02:08:03,400
Excuse me.. who's the
patient's father?

1369
02:08:06,003 --> 02:08:07,129
Yes..?

1370
02:08:07,204 --> 02:08:08,296
Please come

1371
02:08:14,145 --> 02:08:15,271
Sit

1372
02:08:21,352 --> 02:08:24,446
The patient has approximately 40
percent superficial to deep burns,

1373
02:08:26,257 --> 02:08:27,622
third degree burns included

1374
02:08:31,195 --> 02:08:32,685
Luckily, her face was untouched

1375
02:08:37,535 --> 02:08:41,232
Doctor, tomorrow morning,
her bridegroom is arriving

1376
02:08:43,174 --> 02:08:44,641
It is Poonam's wedding tomorrow

1377
02:08:49,413 --> 02:08:53,144
About half of her body is burnt,

1378
02:08:55,619 --> 02:08:56,711
the wounds are deep

1379
02:08:59,657 --> 02:09:01,488
A wedding tomorrow is out of question

1380
02:09:05,629 --> 02:09:09,725
Forgive me for saying.. in such
cases even families abandon their own,

1381
02:09:11,535 --> 02:09:13,127
Iesser said the better.. for someone
who promised to marry her

1382
02:09:19,176 --> 02:09:21,474
Just now, your daughter
is fighting for her life

1383
02:09:24,081 --> 02:09:27,312
Tomorrow morning, as soon as possible,
we must go in for a major surgery

1384
02:09:29,687 --> 02:09:32,588
Now, if you will excuse me, I must
discuss the case with my team

1385
02:09:49,206 --> 02:09:50,468
Krishnakant,

1386
02:09:52,509 --> 02:09:55,171
by now, Prem must be starting out

1387
02:09:57,448 --> 02:09:58,779
We ought to inform..

1388
02:10:42,359 --> 02:10:43,621
Harishchandra quickly! Please

1389
02:10:45,162 --> 02:10:46,288
Sir.. Bhagat

1390
02:10:46,363 --> 02:10:47,728
Yes Bhagat?

1391
02:10:48,299 --> 02:10:51,132
Harishchandra, don't
come here now..

1392
02:11:08,185 --> 02:11:09,277
What happened, Papa?

1393
02:11:13,057 --> 02:11:14,251
Excuse me

1394
02:11:16,093 --> 02:11:18,721
Bhavna, one minute.
- What is it?

1395
02:11:44,621 --> 02:11:45,747
What's the matter Sister-in-law?

1396
02:11:55,699 --> 02:12:00,659
While we are getting ready for surgery
one of you may meet the patient

1397
02:12:05,376 --> 02:12:06,536
Doctor,

1398
02:12:08,345 --> 02:12:11,542
can I see Sister.. even
from far? Please

1399
02:12:14,118 --> 02:12:15,585
Okay, please wait

1400
02:13:11,308 --> 02:13:12,468
Uncle

1401
02:13:15,379 --> 02:13:16,505
Is Chhoti well, Uncle?

1402
02:13:19,116 --> 02:13:20,481
Nothing can harm Chhoti

1403
02:13:23,520 --> 02:13:25,681
No fire can hurt Chhoti

1404
02:13:35,165 --> 02:13:39,431
Tell Aunty, nothing
can harm Chhoti

1405
02:13:43,407 --> 02:13:44,499
Chhoti.. Uncle..

1406
02:14:37,261 --> 02:14:40,662
Look Rama, the bridegroom
has arrived for Poonam

1407
02:14:43,567 --> 02:14:47,128
Look at her palanquin,
so gaily decorated

1408
02:14:50,407 --> 02:14:51,601
Just a while now, then
she will be gone

1409
02:14:55,546 --> 02:14:59,277
Didn't I tell you, you'll cry the most

1410
02:15:02,619 --> 02:15:05,213
It was her beauty that always
pained your eyes,

1411
02:15:07,691 --> 02:15:11,354
so much so, you wouldn't
even look at her

1412
02:15:14,698 --> 02:15:21,399
Look Rama, for our Chhoti's sake,
she has sacrificed her beauty

1413
02:15:25,375 --> 02:15:27,036
Sacrificed her beauty

1414
02:15:38,155 --> 02:15:42,114
Doctor, after the operation, Poonam
will recover fully, won't she?

1415
02:15:43,260 --> 02:15:46,423
Right now, nothing can be said,
it's a very delicate case

1416
02:15:50,400 --> 02:15:52,459
There's more to recovery than
the healing of wounds

1417
02:15:54,671 --> 02:15:57,071
In such cases, one loses
self-confidence

1418
02:15:58,575 --> 02:15:59,667
And the pain in burning..

1419
02:16:01,244 --> 02:16:04,577
you and I cannot imagine,
what that pain is like

1420
02:16:08,151 --> 02:16:11,348
Krishnakant, we're all ready
for Poonam's operation

1421
02:16:12,289 --> 02:16:13,449
It's a major surgery

1422
02:16:16,026 --> 02:16:18,221
I have informed you of the
complications in this case

1423
02:16:19,229 --> 02:16:20,526
Your permission is necessary

1424
02:16:25,135 --> 02:16:26,363
We will try our best

1425
02:16:51,228 --> 02:16:52,991
Two days from now..

1426
02:16:53,063 --> 02:16:55,463
as the clock strikes this hour,
you'll be giving your daughter away

1427
02:17:31,435 --> 02:17:32,527
Uncle

1428
02:17:46,249 --> 02:17:47,375
I will sign

1429
02:18:02,132 --> 02:18:03,997
The wedding will happen today

1430
02:18:04,067 --> 02:18:05,193
Now,

1431
02:18:06,403 --> 02:18:07,734
at the appointed time,

1432
02:18:10,574 --> 02:18:11,666
I seek your permission

1433
02:18:15,145 --> 02:18:16,237
No son,

1434
02:18:18,081 --> 02:18:21,346
your emotions are far-removed
from the reality of things

1435
02:18:21,418 --> 02:18:23,716
You will not be able
to see her in pain

1436
02:18:27,157 --> 02:18:29,091
The girl in pain is not
only your daughter,

1437
02:18:31,094 --> 02:18:32,220
she's also our daughter-in-law

1438
02:18:36,266 --> 02:18:38,496
The best surgeons from
Delhi will be here soon

1439
02:18:39,703 --> 02:18:42,570
Poonam's well-being is
now our responsibility

1440
02:18:43,373 --> 02:18:44,533
Be seated

1441
02:18:49,646 --> 02:18:51,511
Sunil..
- Papa..?

1442
02:18:51,581 --> 02:18:53,208
Come with me. Let's meet Dr Rashid

1443
02:18:57,387 --> 02:18:59,116
May I meet Poonam, Uncle?

1444
02:19:15,071 --> 02:19:16,333
Poonam

1445
02:19:23,280 --> 02:19:25,180
Everything will be fine, Poonam

1446
02:19:34,357 --> 02:19:36,086
Look, what Sister-in-law has sent..

1447
02:19:36,159 --> 02:19:37,649
vermilion for my bride

1448
02:19:45,502 --> 02:19:46,730
It's our wedding today, Poonam

1449
02:20:01,484 --> 02:20:05,352
Sister, leave us alone
for two minutes, please

1450
02:20:14,064 --> 02:20:19,058
Once.. there was a pretty girl
who had a right to that vermilion

1451
02:20:21,104 --> 02:20:25,268
Today's ugly truth..
Iies under this canopy

1452
02:20:28,578 --> 02:20:31,012
Neither am I unawares
of truths Poonam,..

1453
02:20:31,081 --> 02:20:33,276
.. nor are you a stranger
to my intentions

1454
02:20:35,352 --> 02:20:38,185
If you want my love for you to
diminish at this sight of you..

1455
02:20:40,523 --> 02:20:41,615
that is inconceivable, Poonam

1456
02:20:49,432 --> 02:20:55,098
You always prayed for me Poonam and
your prayers were always answered

1457
02:20:58,174 --> 02:20:59,368
Today again.. please pray for me,

1458
02:21:01,444 --> 02:21:06,245
pray, that I find the strength within
me, to never let your faith weaken

1459
02:21:15,325 --> 02:21:20,228
You are my companion, Poonam..
my most beautiful one,

1460
02:21:23,266 --> 02:21:25,063
the one who's always worried,
lest I catch a cold

1461
02:21:27,470 --> 02:21:33,670
One who cares about what I eat,
what I wear, more than I myself

1462
02:21:35,679 --> 02:21:38,011
The one who knows me more
than I know myself

1463
02:21:41,084 --> 02:21:46,078
On our wedding day, l
want from you.. a gift

1464
02:21:51,161 --> 02:21:52,458
Give me all your pain

1465
02:22:11,514 --> 02:22:15,974
Before the auspicious moment goes by,

1466
02:22:16,052 --> 02:22:18,282
Iet the rituals be done

1467
02:22:18,355 --> 02:22:20,983
Let there be no distance..

1468
02:22:21,057 --> 02:22:25,653
between the vermilion
and your forehead

1469
02:22:25,729 --> 02:22:29,995
This is the wedding altar,
the sacred fire,

1470
02:22:30,066 --> 02:22:32,660
the festive home

1471
02:22:34,070 --> 02:22:36,004
At this wedding altar,

1472
02:22:36,072 --> 02:22:38,006
in God's presence,

1473
02:22:38,074 --> 02:22:40,133
in this festive home..

1474
02:22:40,210 --> 02:22:43,008
to anoint you with vermilion..

1475
02:22:43,079 --> 02:22:45,741
I have the right

1476
02:22:48,084 --> 02:22:53,181
I take you as my bride,
I have the right

1477
02:22:53,256 --> 02:22:54,518
Stop

1478
02:22:59,429 --> 02:23:04,128
For once, take off the covers,
look at what I've become

1479
02:23:06,202 --> 02:23:08,363
My love doesn't deserve
this test, Poonam

1480
02:23:10,473 --> 02:23:11,599
And you know it

1481
02:23:42,072 --> 02:23:43,664
Sweets, for everyone.
- Thank you, sir

1482
02:24:00,090 --> 02:24:01,250
Where am I to sign, Doctor?

1483
02:24:06,196 --> 02:24:07,356
Mr Prem,

1484
02:24:09,632 --> 02:24:12,624
in this hospital, so far..

1485
02:24:13,536 --> 02:24:16,027
we've only seen.. brides tortured,
burnt for dowry

1486
02:24:18,608 --> 02:24:22,442
Today, for the first time ever, here..
we've seen someone becoming a bride

1487
02:24:27,150 --> 02:24:31,519
This is Dr Jain, a dear friend. Also,
a famous burns specialist

1488
02:24:32,255 --> 02:24:33,517
And his team.. this is Dr Rashid

1489
02:24:34,157 --> 02:24:36,318
We're here to help you
in any manner we can

1490
02:24:36,392 --> 02:24:39,327
You're most welcome, sir. It's
an honor to have you here

1491
02:24:40,497 --> 02:24:42,226
We've a battle waiting to be won

1492
02:24:44,067 --> 02:24:45,159
Take the new bride to the
operation theater, please

1493
02:24:45,235 --> 02:24:46,327
Please come, Doctor

1494
02:25:23,039 --> 02:25:24,165
Uncle, tea

1495
02:25:25,375 --> 02:25:27,036
No..
- We'll share

1496
02:25:28,545 --> 02:25:30,410
Why are you worrying, Krishnakant?

1497
02:25:32,048 --> 02:25:34,346
He is doing the worrying for
us. You drink your tea

1498
02:25:49,265 --> 02:25:51,392
Thank you so much, Doctor.
Congratulations

1499
02:25:53,503 --> 02:25:55,300
Doctor, how is she?

1500
02:25:55,371 --> 02:25:56,702
Operation successful

1501
02:25:57,073 --> 02:26:01,066
After 48 hours, when bandages come
off, we'll know the exact position

1502
02:26:02,278 --> 02:26:04,109
This first battle we have won, Prem

1503
02:26:06,683 --> 02:26:09,311
For at least a month and a half,
Poonam must stay here

1504
02:26:09,385 --> 02:26:10,443
Doctor..

1505
02:26:12,021 --> 02:26:13,318
Afterwards, she can go home?

1506
02:26:13,389 --> 02:26:14,447
Sure

1507
02:26:14,524 --> 02:26:19,018
Okay, until then, our daughter-in-law
remains in your charge, Krishnakant

